Here is a minimal config that recovers the problem that is on screenshots.
I think you have lightsky.png (try: locate lightsky.png) but any other
image is just good.

  *FvwmPager-Desker: Colorset * 14
  *FvwmPager-Desker: HilightColorset * 15

  Colorset 14 fg white, bg rgb:90/67/64
  Colorset 15 fg rgb:ff/ff/da, bg average, \
