  EdgeScroll 0 0      # good for this test. Why is this not a default?
  Style Fvwm* Sticky  # just to make FvwmConsole and FvwmPager sticky
  FvwmPager FvwmPager-Desker 0 3

Only the current page on the first desk is highlited. On other desks
it looks like transparent that is not refreshed, i.e. if you move or
delete any window you will see its trace like on the first screenshot.
