>     + I Prev (CurrentDesk AcceptsFocus) Function PrevNext
> 
> Key Tab     A   M   Function TabForward

The problem with this is that it can't be canceled by pressed Esc to
return to the window that was focused at the time of Alt-Tab.

Anyway, in 2.5.2 (and partially in 2.4.8, remove IconifiedAtEnd) the
following emulates the Windows behaviour better if anyone likes it:

  Key Tab A M WindowList Root c c CurrentDesk, NoGeometry, CurrentAtEnd, IconifiedAtEnd

Regards,
Mikhael.
